Question: Shenzhen Chifrog Technology Co.,Ltd CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Shenzhen Chifrog Technology Co.,Ltd

Product Highlights at CES 2024:

- CF-W15 Wireless Charger with Alarm Clock
- CH-11 Mini Portable Power Cube
- CH-20 Jump Starter with Air Compressor & Power Station
- PS-D21 Slim Jump Starter Power Bank
- PS-D15 Jump Starter With Wireless Charging
- PS-D26 Slim Jump Starter Power Bank With Compass
- PS-D30 Lite Flashlight Jump Starter
- PS-D30 Plus Flashlight Jump Starter Aluminum Alloy
- CF-A16 Super Jump Starter With Air Compressor
- CH-18 Portable Power Station

Chifrog Technology offers a range of electronic products including wireless chargers, portable power cubes, jump starters with air compressors and power stations, slim power banks with wireless charging and flashlight jump starters. These products are designed for convenience and versatility, providing solutions for charging and power needs.
